{"tid":2428060,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★名潮食館群組】袁國勇揭播毒源頭為茶水間","createTime":"2021-03-01T09:31:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T09:58:58.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1767a989a7404b4bc60465b6ec134daee7c38dac","tid":2428060,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:31:16.000Z","msg":"袁國勇表示，名潮有兩層，包括1樓及地下，特點是所有染疫食客全部屬地下，討論過後相信是短距離空氣傳播引起爆發，最重要原因是因輸送空氣的管很狹窄，鮮風只有正常的三分之一，形容很不理想，空氣流動非常低，故食客很容易中招；另一可能性是，一樓及地下各自有茶水地方，惟地下是所有碗碟是放同一地方，沒有分開乾淨及已使用，若器具或員工的手有感染到，或令茶水受交叉污染。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2889333/【名潮食館群組】袁國勇揭播毒源頭為茶水間%E3%80%80餐廳鮮風傳送只及正常三分一【不斷更新】?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2889333%2F%E3%80%90%E5%90%8D%E6%BD%AE%E9%A3%9F%E9%A4%A8%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84%E3%80%91%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87%E6%8F%AD%E6%92%AD%E6%AF%92%E6%BA%90%E9%A0%AD%E7%82%BA%E8%8C%B6%E6%B0%B4%E9%96%93%25E3%2580%2580%E9%A4%90%E5%BB%B3%E9%AE%AE%E9%A2%A8%E5%82%B3%E9%80%81%E5%8F%AA%E5%8F%8A%E6%AD%A3%E5%B8%B8%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E4%B8%80%E3%80%90%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E3%80%91%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt19Rt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=b56c2e25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2889333/【名潮食館群組】袁國勇揭播毒源頭為茶水間%E3%80%80餐廳鮮風傳送只及正常三分一【不斷更新】?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"c155c8f72e5d9cd9be96d426e53292d1c2917840","tid":2428060,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hcAVLrS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhcAVLrS.jpg&h=e3b487f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"463b73f5bf29c41c6979ed5ef85268e47ecd8646","tid":2428060,"uid":85168,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T09:32:26.000Z","msg":"叫咗 u 咪喺嗰度屙屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac